Wellness Center


Caring For Your Flame


Need Answers? Sign-Up For Our Listserv!






Please complete the form in the link below to be added to our Wellness Center Caring For Your Flame Listserv. By adding your email, you are opting in to receive weekly lifestyle tips and strategies to manage your lifestyle and promote your academic success. You will also receive links to our Caring for Your Flame Mini-Magazine that provides lifestyle hacks.
If at any time you want to opt-out, please send an email to wellnesscenter@uic.edu. 
Our Caring for Your Flame Listserv promotes Wellness Center events, Pop-Up Pantry announcements, FREE giveaways, UIC Resources, and access to campus important reminders. Previous Listserv topics included: How to navigate online classes, stress management, meditation tips and apps, self-care tips, smile enticing videos, UIC resources, and much more. 
We do the research, so you don’t have to!
The Listserv is exclusively for registered UIC students.





Sign-Up For Caring for Your Flame Listserv Here!








